 tools/lib/perf/include/perf/event.h                | 12 +++++++++++
 tools/perf/Documentation/perf.data-file-format.txt | 24 +++++++++++++++++-----
 tools/perf/builtin-record.c                        | 23 ++++++++++++++++-----
